",  "
Facebook
" and "
Tapjoy
".
The Application may use Unity Ads. to serve adverts, users are advised that data may be collected independently by Unity. For full details of Unity's Privacy Policy, please visit,
http://unity3d.com/legal/privacy-policy
The Application may use AdMob Ads. to serve adverts, users are advised that data may be collected independently by AdMob. For full details of AdMob's Privacy Policy, please visit,
https://policies.google.com/privacy
The Application may use AppLovin to serve adverts, users are advised that data may be collected independently by AppLovin. For full details of AppLovin's Privacy Policy, please visit,
https://www.applovin.com/privacy/
The Application may use Flurry Analytics to collect game play data. For full details of Flurry's Privacy Policy, please visit,
https://developer.yahoo.com/flurry/legal-privacy/terms-service/flurry-analytics-terms-service.html
The Application may use Facebook Analytics to collect game play data. For full details of Facebook's Privacy Policy, please visit,
https://www.facebook.com/full_data_use_policy
The Application may use a Tapjoy provided service to serve adverts or offer incentives, users are advised that data may be collected independently by Tapjoy. For full details of Tapjoy's Privacy Policy, please visit,
https://www.tapjoy.com/legal/#privacy-policy
FACEBOOK/FACEBOOK CONNECT
Some of our applications can connect through Facebook to enhance the application and user experience. By using Facebook to connect to your account, you will be providing us with basic account information i.e. user ID and name. We do not cache or store any data we receive from Facebook.
PRIVACY OF CHILDREN
Our applications are not directed at children under the age of 13. Cobra Mobile does not knowingly collect, solicit or store personal information from anyone under the age of 13. We are committed to adhering to the Children's Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA) and EU standards. If you believe that we may have collected information from or about a child under 13, please contact us at, support@cobramobile.com and we will delete such information from our files within a reasonable time.
PRIVACY POLICY CHANGES
This Privacy Policy is subject to change by us at any time. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy regularly for any changes.
CHANGES
Cobra reserves the right at any time to make changes to any section of its Privacy Policy, Terms of Service or License Agreement.
YOUR CONSENT
By using the Application, you are consenting to our processing of your data as set forth in this Privacy Policy now and as amended by us from time to time.
